=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Number_theory#cite_note-32"><span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>30<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>=
 He gave the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euclidean_algorithm" =
