rithm.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMumford2010388_42-0" class=3D"reference">=
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Number_theory#cite_note-FOOTNOTEMu=
mford2010388-42"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>39<span class=3D"cite=
