identities.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-84" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://e=
n.wikipedia.org/wiki/Number_theory#cite_note-84"><span class=3D"cite-bracke=
t">[</span>80<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup></li></ul>
<p>It studies the distribution of primes, behavior of number-theoric functi=
ons, and irrational numbers.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-85" class=3D"reference"><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Number_theory#cite_note-85"><span cla=
